To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private DojiStar _dojistar;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_dojistar = DojiStar(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_dojistar.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "dojistar", _dojistar.Current.Value);
}
